{"tid":2379622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽講港大想起疫苗廠 不服從深圳本部指示","createTime":"2021-01-25T10:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T23:00:52.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdb664989d8fe6903be50cee553b0763eda23de","tid":2379622,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">人地盧寵茂話打中國疫苗就得  香港分部做咩話想搞疫苗廠  係咩想作反 搞港獨</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂深圳接種中國國藥疫苗 稱「很舒服」、「有點興奮」 表明信任中國製造<br />\n<br />\n多間媒體今日（8 日）報道，港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂昨日已於深圳，接種中國國藥集團的武漢肺炎疫苗。據報，<strong>他接種期間表示「很舒服」，接種後則形容自己「有點興奮」</strong>，又說「打好了，我現在有抵抗力了」。他呼籲港府及早計畫安排接種，又指接種疫苗是每個公民的責任，市民應參與。"},{"pid":"f8491bb39d2d4bf441c5d8d0cdbd01e80e3086ac","tid":2379622,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201231/s00002/1609353544886/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00002%2F1609353544886%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=246baaea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00002%2F1609353544886%2F&h=8ab1c8d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201231/s00002/1609353544886/</a>"},{"pid":"54be312fdc77fc3e35b59e19dda22eca5d987c96","tid":2379622,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:36:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c9b78ed15474e580005c556095b0232bef034a8d","tid":2379622,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"他接種期間表示「很舒服」，接種後則形容自己「有點興奮」<br />\n吸毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\